            [
                "Schlemiel",
                "Schiebel"
            ]
        ]
    ],
    "They traveled with Schlegel to Belgium and Switzerland in 1804-05.": [
        [
            19,
            27,
            [
                "Schlemiel",
                "Schiebel"
            ]
        ]
    ],
    "The nationalizing of church property and its destruction through sales greatly alarmed the three.": [],
    "Beginning in 1804 the Boisser\u00e9e brothers began to medieval collect art with as much intent to save it as own it, together with others such as Franz Ferdinand Wallraf (1748-1824).": [
