    "Through the auspices of <a href=\"/quatremeredequincya\">Antoine Quatrem\u00e8re de Quincy</a>, he presented his findings at the <em>Acad\u00e9mie des Beaux-Arts</em> in Paris.": [],
    "After Bertram's death in 1841, he Melchior returned to their Cologne, where they witnessed the resumption of the church construction (beginning in 1842), although the church was not completed until near the end of the century.": [],
    "His autobiography was published in 1862.": [],
    "Sulpiz was one of the founders of modern art-historical studies outside the museum/academic field.": [
