    "His <em>Geschichte und Beschreibung des Domes von K\u00f6ln</em> is the first architectural history.": [],
    "His dedication to classifying art by schools and eras, instead of the \"curiosity jumble\" of previous centuries was important for subsequent historians and museum curators.": [],
    "His confidence in collecting and publicizing underappreciated genres of art places him in the fore of modern art education and collection studies.": [],
